Package: Rflexiplex
Title: Flexible Barcode Demultiplexing for Long-Read RNA-seq
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-07
Authors@R: c(
    person("Changqing", "Wang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "wang.ch@wehi.edu.au"))
Description: Provides flexible barcode demultiplexing for long-read RNA-seq data
    using the flexiplex algorithm. Supports custom barcode segment definitions,
    optional TSO trimming via cutadapt, JSON config loading, and a Shiny-based
    GUI for interactive drag-and-drop barcode segment design.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
