LinkingTo: Rcpp, Rhtslib
SystemRequirements: GNU make, C++17
Config/Bioconductor/UnsupportedPlatforms: windows
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
LazyLoad: yes
